'''Ta-Taka-Ki-Kek''' was a foreign exchange student from Thailand who attended [[Lincoln High School]] with [[Ross Geller]] & [[Will Colbert]]. Together, they formed an [[I Hate Rachel Green Club]], but Ta Taka most likely wasn't aware of what the club was. According to Will, he made out with the Lincoln High School librarian, [[Anita Altman]], the day before he moved back to Thailand.

==Trivia==

*Ross is another student who kissed the Lincoln High librarian, Mrs. Altmann.
